{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"fdab294d-770b-4184-a487-ab84cc959e56","content":"This is a well-known MTP behavioral difference. **MTP returns exit code 8 when zero tests are discovered**, whereas VSTest returned 0. Since all your tests are behind `#if INCLUDE_SLOW_TESTS`, configurations without that symbol produce zero tests → exit code 8.\n\n**Fix:** Tell MTP to treat \"no tests found\" as success. Add this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>\n```\n\nLet me apply it:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01ABEMWaiZXK23qkcS9fvSby","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Fixing MTP exit code"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_012N8kusKWCvvNzJ1QiMCYdL","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-06e6ef2f54094a21a5120ffc390c5626/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n    <TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-06e6ef2f54094a21a5120ffc390c5626/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"2b876136-9580-405c-8d96-c4e17ffb8c96","outputTokens":405,"requestId":"1BCA:13C87:AC5BE4:C4201E:6A03CF18"},"id":"31f5f0b9-cae1-4feb-b6be-0029c14d278d","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:08:46.501Z","parentId":"011eb850-3081-44c4-b4b1-0fdb3fb4f49c"}
